that was my experience at least, at higher levels aes seem to be more for AE specifc groups in an attempt to gain fast loot exp, but i honestly havent used aes too much <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/unaladini.showPublicProfile?language=EN>naladini</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Arch Mage</span><br>  Posts: 443<br> <font color=#333333>(9/24/02 5:58:13 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1558.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: LVL 27 MAGE</span><hr size=1> Just make sure you wait until pet has taunted twice before casting a dmg spell if you are going to use a rain.<br>
<br>
IF all 3 waves hit, they can be more potent than comparable DD/Bolt spells in terms of mana ratio.<br>
<br>
